A cyberpunk cityscape at night where streams of glowing binary data and compact geometric packets race through translucent fiber optic tubes that weave between towering server monoliths. In the foreground, two distinct data streams merge at a junction point - one stream composed of dense, tightly-packed crystalline cubes representing binary protocol data, the other flowing as looser, more organic curly-bracket-shaped particles suggesting JSON structures. The tubes pulse with neon blue and electric orange light, casting reflections on rain-slicked streets below. Holographic circuit patterns shimmer in the atmosphere. The scene conveys speed, efficiency, and the invisible infrastructure of modern digital communication, with a sense of data racing at impossible velocities through an interconnected network architecture.
